# 22. Mathematical Intuition

Suppose Dubai has two revenue values:

[
1000,\ 1500
]

Total revenue:

[
1000 + 1500 = 2500
]

Average revenue:

[
\frac{1000 + 1500}{2} = 1250
]

Grouping performs the following process:

```text
Split data into groups
        |
        v
Apply calculation to each group
        |
        v
Combine the results
```

This is often described as:

```text
Split → Apply → Combine
```

